1
00:00:59,000 --> 00:00:59,240
Hello,

2
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:03,119
you don't have to do nothing every day, right?

3
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,159
This is something.

4
00:01:06,599 --> 00:01:07,079
How happy!

5
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:08,760
It's not your happiness.

6
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,200
Qi Qi can only be mine.

7
00:01:11,239 --> 00:01:12,159
Chumo, let me tell you,

8
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,799
how you live your life

9
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,480
has nothing to do with me.

10
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:15,799
Yes, I understand.

11
00:01:17,519 --> 00:01:18,400
But,

12
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:22,879
Qi is a girl

13
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:24,760
who is hard to find.

14
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:15,680
What's wrong?

15
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,080
I want to drink juice.

16
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:20,439
What juice?

17
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:22,120
Orange juice, okay?

18
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:22,599
Okay.

19
00:02:23,199 --> 00:02:24,240
Bring me a bottle of cold juice.

20
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,360
I'm leaving.

21
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:35,560
What do you want to tell me?

22
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,479
I'm too busy to get rid of Jiang Yue.

23
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,319
I haven't figured out how to comfort him.

24
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:43,080
I don't have the right to say anything.

25
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:45,879
Lu Qi,

26
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:48,800
you can get rid of Jiang Yue once,

27
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,080
but he won't let you do it twice.

28
00:02:52,439 --> 00:02:53,680
If he comes back later,

29
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:54,919
you won't have a chance to say it.

30
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:57,360
I don't know if you remember.

31
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,840
One day,

32
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,360
it rained heavily.

33
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:05,039
You know what?

34
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,319
I envy you.

35
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,879
Because your soul is light.

36
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,680
I thought it was because

37
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,800
you don't care

38
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,879
what people say.

39
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,439
But now I don't think so.

40
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,520
Now

41
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,080
you think I'm cold and heartless.

42
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:26,759
No.

43
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:28,680
On the contrary,

44
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,919
I think

45
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:33,080
you have strong emotions.

46
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:36,080
Like the spring hidden in the rock crevices,

47
00:03:36,759 --> 00:03:38,840
not noisy, but very clear.

48
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,439
You are very serious and pure

49
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,719
to the people and things you recognize.

50
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,439
You give people a warm feeling,

51
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,039
and make people want to get close.

52
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,520
Maybe

53
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,280
you've been hurt badly before,

54
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:55,840
so

55
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:59,000
you've closed off your emotions.

56
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,199
So,

57
00:04:07,639 --> 00:04:08,800
are you worried about me?

58
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,240
Sort of.

59
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:17,720
Don't worry.

60
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,680
A man

61
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,120
with money,

62
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,759
time,

63
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:25,680
and youth like me

64
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,439
can't possibly live poorly.

65
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:30,120
Instead of worrying about me,

66
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,879
you'd better worry about yourself.

67
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:37,720
After all, we are similar.

68
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:44,839
No.

69
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,439
I have a father.

70
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,120
He gave me warmth.

71
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:55,360
I have a mother.

72
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:57,920
She taught me patience.

73
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,160
And I have Jiang Yue.

74
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,519
He tries his best

75
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:05,759
to lift me up to the sun.

76
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:10,079
Actually, these are the most

77
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:12,439
ordinary emotions in the world.

78
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,160
But you know what?

79
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:17,680
Often,

80
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,959
in many cases,

81
00:05:21,279 --> 00:05:22,680
these ordinary emotions

82
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,399
can be

83
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,160
very luxurious.

84
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:33,000
You must never have had these.

85
00:05:35,519 --> 00:05:36,319
So,

86
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:39,879
you became a butterfly.

87
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:57,720
Lu Qi,

88
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:01,519
you're quite quick

89
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:04,120
at seducing people.

90
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,759
I... I know I was wrong.

91
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,800
I really know I was wrong.

92
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,040
I...

93
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:26,560
You...

94
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:29,519
Can you forgive me?

95
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,560
I want to be nice to you.

96
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:33,480
I really want to be nice to you this time.

97
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:05,800
You can't talk to me at night, can you?

98
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,120
Qi Qi's eyes are almost fully recovered.

99
00:07:13,319 --> 00:07:14,199
Thank you

100
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,319
for your help.

101
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:22,680
I'm leaving.

102
00:07:24,759 --> 00:07:25,160
Leaving?

103
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:27,399
Where are you going?

104
00:07:30,759 --> 00:07:31,279
To see Qi Qi.

105
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:43,279
First Jiang Changfa,

106
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,800
now Lu Qi.

107
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:47,600
Jiang Yue,

108
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,560
haven't you ever thought about living for yourself?

109
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,800
I love Qi.

110
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,879
She is my life.

111
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:06,680
I know it very well.

112
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:09,680
I love her.

113
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:16,759
Forget it.

114
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,720
Don't wait until later.

115
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,800
Come out and walk with me.

116
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:23,199
It's too stuffy in this room.

117
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:02,639
I want to take Qi away.

118
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,159
If you leave,

119
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,039
Jiang Changfa will stop chasing you.

120
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:17,080
Jiang Yue,

121
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,840
I believe you have the ability to do it.

122
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,759
But only when he dies,

123
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,799
you and Lu Qi can live a stable life.

124
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:29,879
If you can't do it,

125
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,159
I can help you.

126
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:34,399
No need.

127
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:37,879
What do you mean?

128
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,320
After all, he's my father.

129
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,000
I don't understand

130
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,159
your twisted feelings.

131
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,840
But to make you less twisted,

132
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,360
I can tell you something.

133
00:09:59,879 --> 00:10:01,159
The reason Wang Yuhe came to me

134
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,679
is that he really couldn't figure out

135
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:06,720
what exactly 3Z did 16 years ago

136
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,720
that could make him suppress Black Snow

137
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,480
for over a decade.

138
00:10:12,159 --> 00:10:13,039
16 years ago,

139
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,720
the year my mother died.

140
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:21,759
What did you find?

141
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:22,840
Totem.

142
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:27,840
You want to know what it means, don't you?

143
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,120
Otherwise, you wouldn't have looked into

144
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,120
Andrew Bell.

145
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,159
Dirty and bloody.

146
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:35,840
That's right.

147
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:39,240
It's the mark of a minor leader

148
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,480
of human trafficking.

149
00:10:41,559 --> 00:10:43,279
Every minor leader who comes into contact with the totem

150
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:44,840
will sign an indenture.

151
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:46,840
After signing,

152
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,919
they will get a key

153
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:49,559
known only to the grantor

154
00:10:49,799 --> 00:10:51,559
and the grantee,

155
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:54,000
which is used for their transactions on the Dark Web.

156
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:55,960
Human trafficking?

157
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:58,440
The key of the death contract?

158
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:05,120
Sixteen years ago, your mother died in the fire.

159
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:07,240
Your father suddenly became rich.

160
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:10,919
Is it a coincidence?

161
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:14,720
Jiang Yue,

162
00:11:16,279 --> 00:11:18,559
the father you're still defending,

163
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,320
is involved in human trafficking.

164
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,759
The blood on his hands

165
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:26,159
must include your mother's.

166
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:30,919
I'll say it one last time,

167
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:33,960
I can help you,

168
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,759
but I won't.

169
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,600
I'll find out the truth

170
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,840
about my mother's death myself.

171
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:47,759
Investigate it yourself?

172
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,519
What about Lu Qi?

173
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,200
Are you taking her with you?

174
00:11:58,759 --> 00:11:59,559
That's not safe.

175
00:12:09,519 --> 00:12:09,879
Tell me.

176
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,120
I sent Qi Qi's "Tearing" to Florensa.

177
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:30,000
SP promised to give her the Best Newcomer Award.

178
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,039
SP

179
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:39,559
is not as good as Müller,

180
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:40,960
but it's about the same.

181
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:42,840
Pretty good.

182
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:52,960
Do you like her?

183
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,200
I really like that kind...

184
00:12:58,759 --> 00:12:59,200
I don't understand.

185
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,279
If you like her, you should take good care of her.

186
00:13:07,159 --> 00:13:08,279
Send her abroad to receive awards.

187
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,240
Send her to school.

188
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,039
Protect her well.
